能下降。对于那些对 Prime 不感兴趣的人，我们还列出了本周与该活动没有明确关联的一些最佳科技交易。随着 Prime Day 的临近，我们将继续关注，并在新优惠出现时更新本综述。</p><h2>亚马逊 Fire 电视棒 4K Max </h2><p><core-commerce id="eda7678048654afcb618ece113f5421b" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>亚马逊<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUZ87ioBg75ZQWUJoBAcVDH7N1-ZlL-_oq88Eoyluc-N&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Ffire-tv-stick-4k-max-with-alexa-voice-remote%2Fdp%2FB08MQZXN1X">Fire TV Stick 4K Max</a>在 Prime 会员日之前已降至 25 美元，比正常价格低一半以上，并创下历史新低。这是亚马逊制造的最强大的流媒体加密狗，具有比标准<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAV2pDAt1LyO6ghSYXJ-C4TJONCc0P2CjmErvn1BrIbAx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fall-new-fire-tv-stick-4k-with-alexa-voice-remote%2Fdp%2FB08XVYZ1Y5" class="rapid-with-clickid">Fire TV Stick 4K</a>更出色的处理器，并且支持 WiFi 6、杜比视界、HDR10+ 和杜比全景声音频。虽然与 Roku、谷歌和苹果的其他平台相比，亚马逊的 Fire TV 操作系统可能比较混乱，但它仍然可以让您访问几乎所有主要的流媒体应用程序。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbWzzNGgqt-Tor0GIFqaXtvr3278yWWPMkMye9gZBn45&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdeal%2Ffdc2ebbc%3FshowVariations%3Dtrue%26pf_rd_r%3DHPGFH1RAQB9GGBM79X5W%26pf_rd_t%3DEvents%26pf_rd_i%3Ddeals%26pf_rd_p%3Da104a363-1843-4010-8c3f-063171c49447%26pf_rd_s%3Dslot-14%26ref%3Ddlx_deals_gd_dcl_img_1_fdc2ebbc_dt_sl14_47">其他一些 Fire 流媒体设备</a>也打折，包括最新的<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteI