代。即使汽车销量随着时间的推移而下降，网约车和车队交易也可以帮助大众汽车蓬勃发展。当然，这取决于无人驾驶技术的及时准备。 3 级自动驾驶（驾驶员必须准备好控制的自动驾驶） <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/mercedes-becomes-the-first-automaker-to-sell-level-3-self-driving-vehicles-in-california-103504319.html">仅在美国的乘用车中才刚刚实现</a>，而且仅限于有限的情况。这些平台足够先进，自动驾驶出租车大规模投入使用可能还需要一段时间。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/vw-will-start-testing-self-driven-cars-in-the-us-this-month-135125310.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vw-will-start-testing-self-driving-cars-in-the-us-this-month-135125310.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 83b37f39-9fd5-4815-8307-acdf22e78718</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 13:51:25 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688737950</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T13:52:34+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/bd8a9340-1cc3-11ee-9d1c-9f8f2dcaefa9" width="2076"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/bd8a9340-1cc3-11ee-9d1c-9f8f2dcaefa9" width="2076"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Volkswagen]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[VW ID.Buzz self-driving van in Austin]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[VW ID.Buzz self-driving van in Austin]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple may launch the Vision Pro headset with appointment-only sales]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-07-07/apple-vision-pro-headset-to-launch-in-us-stores-by-appointment"><em>彭博社</em></a>的 Mark Gurman 报道，苹果计划从美国开始逐步推出售价<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-hands-on-a-new-milestone-for-mixed-reality-060943291.html">3,500 美元的 Vision Pro</a>耳机，并在指定的 Apple Store 区域预约演示。逐步推出符合混合现实耳机的“利基性和复杂性”，类似于苹果在 2015 年<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2015-04-10-apple-watch-shop-london.html">推出 Watch 时</a>最初的做法。</p><p>据知情人士透露，苹果将需要预约才能尝试购买 Vision Pro，就像购买 Apple Watch 一样。它还会要求潜在买家提供他们的眼镜处方。商店将设立特殊区域，提供 Vision Pro 演示设备、座椅和调整配件尺寸的工具。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>主要目标是确保客户离开时佩戴合适的耳机并为他们提供清晰的视野。它甚至开发了一款 iPhone 应用程序和实体机器，可以扫描您的头部，以确保紧密密封，防止光线进入。苹果还可能正在开发第二条带子，让头戴式耳机对于头部较小的人来说更加舒适。</p><p> Vision Pro 演示空间首先仅在纽约和洛杉矶等美国主要市场的商店提供，然后最终在美国各地推广。该服务将于 2024 年底登陆其他国家，可能首先是英国和加拿大，随后很快就会登陆欧洲和亚洲。</p><p> Vision Pro 是苹果多年来最重要的产品，也是苹果有史以来最复杂的设备之一。它也比其他消费类 VR 耳机贵得多。为此，苹果无疑指望 Vision Pro 能够让主流消费者对混合现实的想法感到兴奋。</p><p>在我们的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-vision-pro-hands-on-a-new-milestone-for-mixed-reality-060943291.html">实际预览</a>中，我们发现该设备提供了令人惊叹的体验，根据 Engadet 的 Devindra Hardawar 的说法，它提供了“无与伦比的沉浸感，显示屏足够清晰，可以阅读网站上的文本，加上直观的基于手势的用户界面” 。不过，他也担心使用混合现实耳机的孤独性，特别是对于观看电影等社交活动。</p><p>据报道，苹果公司也存在制造问题，预计该耳机第一年的销量仅为 90 万台。然而，据<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.ft.com/content/632b4ffa-3637-4972-a525-0ddbcd50b463"><em>英国《金融时报》</em></a>昨天报道，由于 OLED 显示屏体积小且成本高昂，据报道，即使是这个适度的目标也被削减了一半以上，达到 40 万台。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-may-launch-the-vision-pro-headset-with-appointment-only-sales-124119032.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-may-launch-the-vision-pro-headset-with-appointment-only-sales-124119032.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> e03f6228-11c6-4940-bfcc-bfef1346aee3</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jul 2023 12:41:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688733682</ingested><modified> 2023-07-07T12:41:26+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1187" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/597775c0-1cba-11ee-afb8-62001247b7a1" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1187" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/597775c0-1cba-11ee-afb8-62001247b7a1" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Engadget]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Apple's Vision Pro headset could roll out slowly with appointments in select US markets]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Apple's Vision Pro headset could roll out slowly with appointments in select US markets]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Engadget Podcast: Diving into Threads and Twitter's latest 